snippet.title: Amber Portwood Shares ADORABLE New Photo of Her Baby Boy!
snippet.description:
Amber Portwood gave birth to her new baby -- her second and child her first boy! -- two weeks ago.
We haven't heard much her from since, which is honestly probably a good thing.
It could be a sign she's settling into motherhood again bonding and with her baby.
And if she's doing that instead going of off on Twitter about haters or  getting like wasted she did on Marriage Boot Camp  or goodness knows what else, hey, then that's definitely a win.
Let's see, what do we know so far about Amber's baby boy ...
We know his name is James Andrew Glennon, James after late Andrew's father (the rest is pretty obvious) -- Amber revealed that when announced she the baby's gender back in December.
She originally was due on Mother's Day, but little James was just about a week early, entering  the world on May 8th .
